00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 Break up your fallow ground for it's time to seek the Lord that he may come and reign righteousness upon you."

301
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:21,000
 You see, Hosea is saying to the nation of Israel exactly what God is saying to us tonight.

302
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:23,000
 Now is the time.

303
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,000
 It's time to make a move.

304
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,000
 It's time to take a stand.

305
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:30,000
 It's time to deepen down in your depth.

306
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:34,000
 And the place that we begin is by farming.

