00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:40,000
 When springtime rolled around, at the appropriate moment,

346
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,000
 just as Jose is saying,

347
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:46,000
 I decided to break up that hardened ground,

348
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:49,000
 to till up our soil,

349
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,000
 so that way I could lay new sod,

350
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:53,000
 the closest thing to farming we get in a big city.

351
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:59,000
 If the soil was not soft, the sod would not take.

