00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:57,000
 Several years ago, I was at the gym and I was training legs.

570
00:30:57,000 --> 00:31:00,000
 Fellas, don't skip leg day.

571
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:03,000
 As I was doing it, I felt my back tweak.

572
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:07,000
 And so, being a wise and responsible adult, I put the weights down,

573
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:09,000
 picked up a yoga mat, and I said, "I'm going to stretch this thing out."

574
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:11,000
 So I make my way over, and I start to stretch everything out,

575
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,000
 and I feel fine by the end of it.

576
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:16,000
 I get in my car, I go home, I've got a couple of boxes to unload at the house,

577
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:19,000
 and as I'm putting these boxes down, I bend over to set one to the ground,

578
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,000
 and I went with it.

579
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:26,000
 My knees buckled, I found myself face down on the ground,

580
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,000
 and I genuinely could not move.

581
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:32,000
 I had fallen and I could not get back up, yet I had no life alert to save me.

582
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:38,000
 I army crawled my way into the house, where I laid on a couch, immobile, for three days.

583
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:42,000
 It was at that time that my wife, being the voice of wisdom,

584
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,000
 looked at me and said, "We should do something about this."

585
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:47,000
 "No, baby, it's going to be fine. Just let me sleep it off."

586
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:51,000
 "No, really, we should do something about this. I can't keep changing your clothes for you,

587
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:54,000
 because you can't bend over to pull your pants up."

588
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:57,000
 It was a moment of great humility.

589
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:59,000
 And so we went to the local urgent care.

590
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:03,000
 Walked in, they gave me a steroid shot, they also recommended physical therapy.

591
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:06,000
 I was back to 100%, so I went back.

592
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:10,000
 Ten months later, I found myself back on the ground.

593
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,000
 Why?

594
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:15,000
 Because I did not sow into my health.

595
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:17,000
 I didn't go to physical therapy.

596
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,000
 I didn't do my stretches.

597
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:24,000
 I didn't work on my mobility.

598
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:26,000
 I sowed into my hurt.

599
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:31,000
 I went right back to doing what I had always done.

600
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:37,000
 Listen, you cannot sow the same seed and expect a different result.

601
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:40,000
 You cannot sow the same seed and expect a different result.

602
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,000
 That's not how this works.

603
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,000
 If you want to experience more of God in your life,

604
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:47,000
 then you need to make different decisions in your life.

605
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:51,000
 So let me ask you, do the hard work of evaluating where you sit.

